台灣大學寫作教學中心-學術英文口頭報告














學術英文口頭報告


課程大綱


概述
English Presentations for Academic Purposes: This course is designed for graduate students who seek
          training and/or improvement in their English-language presentation skills for
          academic purposes.  


課程目標
The goals of this course are mainly to develop
          speaking and presentation skills in the following areas: 

          How to speak like a professional 
          Effective use of PowerPoint 
          Professional ethos, image, and identity 
          Presenting scientific (or other) research and findings 

          Depending on the actual needs of the enrolled students, the following areas
          may be added: 
          Case studies 
          Demonstration lessons 
          Formal speeches 
          Individual/group presentations 
          Oral exams/Defense of papers 
          Poster presentations 
           


課程要求

This course is open only to graduate students. The
          course is entirely taught in English and all materials are in English. No
          auditors allowed. 




課程進度




週次
日期
